description:String: Can see all product artifacts. Can create/modify all artifacts. Can access the product/template administration tools
Can see all product artifacts. Can create/modify all artifacts
Can see all product artifacts (except automation hosts). Can create new and modify your own risks and incidents. Can create and modify all / bulk edit documents, tasks, and tests
Can see all product artifacts (except tasks). Can create new and modify your own risks and tests. Can create and modify all / bulk edit documents, incidents, and automation hosts
Can see all product artifacts, but cannot perform any write operations (create / modify / delete)
Can only create/modify/view incidents and their attachments that you are the owner of. Cannot see anything else (cannot see requirements, tests, risks, or releases)
